vibeos-desktop (2.0.0-day9c) noble; urgency=medium

  * Plymouth PNGs re-rendered as PNG32 (RGBA). Indexed 8-bit PNGs
    may have been silently misrendered by libply on some Plymouth
    builds.

 -- Mats Mjåtvedt <matswm86@yahoo.no>  Fri, 17 Apr 2026 01:00:00 +0200

vibeos-desktop (2.0.0-day9b) noble; urgency=medium

  * Plymouth: drop Image.Text(), ship pre-rendered wordmark.png +
    tagline.png per theme (rendered at deb build via ImageMagick +
    bundled Orbitron TTF). Fixes the "blurry / overlapping lines"
    Pacific Dawn splash on MSI — initramfs had no fontconfig cache
    matching the runtime, so Image.Text drifted. PNGs remove all
    font-at-boot dependency.

 -- Mats Mjåtvedt <matswm86@yahoo.no>  Fri, 17 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0200

vibeos-desktop (2.0.0-day5) noble; urgency=medium

  * Add three additional KDE Look-and-Feel packages:
    - org.vibeos.outrun  (synthwave: violet + magenta + cyan)
    - org.vibeos.miami   (pastel: peach + coral + teal)
    - org.vibeos.neon-grid (black chrome: neon green + cyan)
  * Add matching color schemes: VibeOS-Outrun, VibeOS-Miami, VibeOS-NeonGrid.
  * Add three wallpaper packs (3 time-of-day variants each, rendered from SVG).
  * Add three Plymouth boot splashes matching each theme.
  * Add four Konsole color schemes (Pacific Dawn + three new themes).
  * Ship /usr/bin/vibeos-theme-switch wrapper for safe lookandfeeltool calls.

 -- Mats Mjåtvedt <matswm86@yahoo.no>  Wed, 15 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0200

vibeos-desktop (2.0.0-day2) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial Pacific Dawn branding package (v2 Day 2).
  * KDE Look-and-Feel package org.vibeos.pacific-dawn.
  * Color scheme VibeOS-PacificDawn.
  * Three Pacific Dawn wallpapers (sunrise / noon / dusk).
  * Plymouth boot splash vibeos-pacific-dawn.
  * SDDM Breeze overrides using Pacific Dawn palette.
  * Orbitron + JetBrains Mono fonts.
  * VibeOS /etc/os-release.

